SECRET FOR FINAL: WHEN DOING FINAL, THE NUMBER WILL WORK OUT TO A WHOLE NUMBER,
  IF YOU GET A FRACTION YOU MADE A MISTAKE

Undercapitalization: You ran out of money, dont have enough money to run the corporation
  They cant execute a new ad campaign or conduct a new research

Understand difference between secured and unecured credit

Secured: Has callateral, When you as a lender make a loan to someone, and you have the right to 
  take something if they dont pay back
    Ex: Reposess you car / house if you ont pay
Unsecured: Does not have callateral
  Ex: Student loan, the govt cant take away your education
  As a result for not being callateral, they have a higher interest rate 

